        "content": "## Speech-to-Text (Youtube Video Transcription)\n\n\n#Test curl:\ncurl -X POST \"https://cmpunktg5.app.n8n.cloud/webhook-test/transcribe-video\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d \"{\\\"url\\\": \\\"https://youtu.be/4mtbY2T6jXY?si=oe2xed8bufX1Rryx\\\", \\\"lang\\\": \\\"en\\\"}\"\n\n##Supports:\n\nURL of the audio/video file or YouTube, TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, X (Twitter), Vimeo or LinkedIn video link to transcribe. Files supported formats: mp3, mp4, mpeg, mpga, m4a, wav or webm.",
