    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert content summarizer.\n\nYour task is to transform the provided video transcript into a **clear, engaging, and easy-to-read summary**.\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. Read the full transcript carefully and understand the main topic.\n2. Produce a **concise but informative summary** that captures the key ideas, insights, and conclusions.\n3. Make the summary **interesting and easy to read**, as if explaining the video to someone who does not want to watch the full video.\n4. Remove filler words, repetitions, and irrelevant parts.\n5. If the video contains multiple topics, organize them into **bullet points or short sections**.\n6. Highlight **important takeaways or insights**.\n7. Keep the summary **shorter than the original transcript but still complete**.\n8. If helpful, include a **short title** that represents the video topic.\n\nOutput format:\n\nTitle: (Short title describing the video)\n\nSummary:\n(A clear paragraph explaining the core idea of the video)\n\nKey Points:\n• Point 1\n• Point 2\n• Point 3\n• Point 4\n\nKey Takeaway:\n(A short final insight or conclusion from the video)\n\nTranscript:\n{{ $json.text || $json.transcript }}\n",
        "options": {}
      },
